\h Filipai
\toc3 FL
\toc2 Filipai
\toc1 Ak…®nafarir Pol Filipain Nguibam…®n Itir Sios Bagha Osirizim
\mt1 Ak…®nafarir Pol Filipain Nguibam…®n Itir Sios Bagha Osirizim
\mt2 O
\mt1 Filipai
\imt1 Akar faragh zuim
\ip Pol faragha kurim…®n ongarim…®n ghua faragha Yurop…®n danganim…®n otogha, Masedonian Provins…®n aven itir nguibar ekiam Filipain ghua, Akar Aghuim akuri (Aposel 16:8-15). A g…®n ghua nguibar igharazim…®n itima me a kalabus gat…®. Ez…® a kalabus…®n ikia orazima gumazir maba Filipain itir Krais…®n adarazir n…®ghn…®zir gavgavibagh as…®ghas…®ghasava ami. E Pol Filipaiba bagha amadazir ak…®nafarir kam…®n gara fo, bizir kaba Pol gamima an osemezir pu. Puvat…®. A n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Iesus…®n ikia, egha bar akuegha iti.
\ip Pol faragha bar dag…®abar otefe, ez…® Filipaiba an akurvaghasa dag…®aba a bagha da amada. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Pol ak…®nafarir kam…®n Filipaiba a gamizir bizim bagha me m…®nabi. Egha uaghan a men n…®ghn…®zir gavgaviba, gavgavim dar an…®ngasa. A kamagh…®n aghua, me Pol…®n m…®k…®m suam, gumaka, a kalabus…®n ikiama, egh me n…®ghn…®zir av…®ribar amuva os…®mam.
\ip Pol bizir aghuir God me gan…®ngizim…®n me m…®gei, kar ik…®r…®m…®rir igiar me Krais Iesus ko porogha inizim. A ghaze, me Moses Osirizir Arazibar g…®n ghua bizir aghuir kam inizir puvat…®. Me n…®ghn…®zir gavgavimra Iesus…®n ikia egha a ini. Pol kamaghsua, Filipaiba Krais…®n arazibar g…®n mangam. Krais kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®, a uab…® gumazir ekiam, egha uab…® uan ifongiam…®n g…®n zuir puvat…®. A uab…® d…®kab…®ragha God a gan…®ngizir ingangarir kam gami. Pol kamagh…®n m…®gei, gumazamizir bar Krais ko poroghav itiba, me God…®n navir am…®rizim isi, egha bar akueghav…®ra iti.
\ip E ak…®nafarir kam…®n gara fo, Pol Filipain nguibar ekiam…®n itir sios…®n gumazamiziba bar me gifonge.
\c 1
\ms1 Filipain gumazamiziba bar derav…®ra Pol ko ingarima a bar akonge
\mr (Sapta 1--4)
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 1:1 \xt Aposel 16:12-40\x*Pol ko Timoti, Krais Iesus…®n ingangarir gumazimning, ga, ia God…®n gumazamizir Filipain nguibar ekiam…®n itiba bagha ak…®nafarir kam osiri. Ia Krais Iesus…®n poroghav iti. Ia ko ian tong…®n itir gumazamizir dapaniba ko sios…®n ingangarir gumazamiziba, ga bar ia bagha osiri.
\v 2 \x - \xo 1:2 \xt Rom 1:7; Galesia 1:3; Filemon 1:3\x*E ghaze, God en Afeziam, ko Ekiam Krais Iesus, aning ian apangkuvigh…®va, ia damut…® ia navir am…®rizim…®n ik…®.
\s1 Pol God ko m…®g…®ava a m…®nabi
\p 
\v 3 \x - \xo 1:3 \xt Rom 1:8; 1 Korin 1:4; Efesus 1:15-16\x*Dughiabar k…® ia g…®n…®ghn…®gha, ia bagha uan God m…®nabi.
\v 4-5 Dughiar faragha zuim…®n ghua iza dat…®r…®k…®n, ia nan akurvagha na ko Akar Aghuim…®n ingangarim gami. Kamagh…®n, dughiar k…® ia bagha God ko m…®geiba, k…® zurara bar akonge.
\v 6 \x - \xo 1:6 \xt Jon 6:29; 1 Korin 1:8; Filipai 1:10; 2:13; 1 Tesalonika 1:3\x*Ez…® k…® kamagh…®n fo, God uab…® ingangarir kam ia gan…®ga, ian navir averiabar aven ingar mang…®, Krais Iesus Ua Izamin Dughiam…®n ingangarir kam ag…®vagham.
\p 
\v 7 K…® uan navir averiam…®n aven bar ia gifuegha ia g…®n…®ghn…®ghav…®ra iti. Dat…®r…®gh…®n dughiar k…® kalabus…®n itim, ko dughiar faragha k…® pura itim, k…® Akar Aghuim deragha a m…®g…®a gumazamizibagh amima me fo, Akar Aghuim a bar guizbang…®ra, egha n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an iti. God uan apangkuvim…®n ingangarir kam na gan…®ngiz…®ma, ia bar nan akurvagha na ko ingari. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, bar deragha k…® n…®ghn…®zir aghuir kam ian iti.
\v 8 \x - \xo 1:8 \xt Rom 1:9\x*God kamagh…®n fo, Krais Iesus…®n apangkuvim uab…® nan navim gamima k…® bar ian ganasa bar ifonge.
\p 
\v 9 \x - \xo 1:9 \xt 1 Tesalonika 3:12; Filemon 1:6\x*Ez…® k…® zurara kamagh…®n God ko m…®g…®a ghaze, arazir igharaz darazigh ifongezim, a ian ik…®va aghung…®va ekevegh mang…®v…®ra ik…®. Eght…® ia fofozir ekiam ik…®va, ian n…®ghn…®ziba bar d…®k…®r…®migham.
\v 10 \x - \xo 1:10 \xt Rom 12:2; Efesus 5:10; Filipai 1:6; 2:16; 1 Tesalonika 3:13; Hibru 5:14\x*K…® ghaze, ia derav…®ra araziba bar dar gan da tuis…®gh arazir aghuibar g…®n mang…®. Eght…® Krais Ua Izamin Dughiam…®n, ia God…®n damazim…®n bar zuegh ik…®t…® arazir kuratam ian poroghan kogham.
\v 11 Eght…® arazir aghuir Krais Iesus ami otiviba, da bar ia giz…®vagham. Eght…® gumazamiziba dar gan…®va ziar ekiam God dan…®ng…®va egh an ziam fam. Kamagh…®n, k…® ia bagha God ko m…®gei.
\s1 Pol kalabus…®n iti, ez…® bizir kam Akar Aghuim…®n akurvasi
\p 
\v 12 \x - \xo 1:12 \xt 2 Timoti 2:9\x*Nan adarasi, k…® ia foghasa, na batozir bizir kaba da Akar Aghuim…®n anogorozir puvat…®. An Akar Aghuim gamima a ghuav…®ra iti.
\v 13 \x - \xo 1:13 \xt Aposel 28:30; Efesus 3:1\x*Kamagh…®n m…®dorozir gumazir Rom…®n atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n gariba ko gumazir igharaziba sara, me bar kamagh…®n fogha g…®fa, k…® Krais…®n ingangarim gamima, me bizir kam bagha na isa kalabus gat…®.
\v 14 Ez…® en adarazir av…®riba oraki, k…® kalabus…®n iti, ez…® me na g…®n…®ghn…®si. Ez…® bizir kam gavgavim men navibagh an…®dima me n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Ekiam…®n iti. Egha me atiatir arazim atagh…®ragha bar gavgavigha God…®n akam akura ghuav…®ra iti.
\p 
\v 15 Guizbang…®ra, marazi gumazamizibar garima, me ziar ekiam na gan…®dima, men naviba nan ikuvigha na d…®kab…®nasa. Egha kamagh…®n me Krais…®n akam akuri. Ez…® marazi me n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba ikiava akam akuri.
\v 16 Gumazamizir kaba me fo, God ingangarim na gan…®ga na m…®sefe, ingangarir kam an Akar Aghuim deragha an gun m…®geir ingangarim, ez…® bizir kam…®n k…® kalabus…®n iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me bar na gifonge, egha akam akuri.
\v 17 Ez…® gumazamizir igharazir k…® faragha m…®geiba, me uari ziar ekiaba iniasa, egha Krais…®n akam akuri. Me guiz…®n n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba puvat…®gha kamagh…®n ami. Me kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, k…® kalabus…®n itir dughiam…®n me uam os…®mt…®zir taba na dar…®ghasa.
\v 18 Ez…® a pura bizim. Me n…®ghn…®zir aghuim iti, o n…®ghn…®zir kuram iti, gumazamizir kaba zurara Krais…®n akam akuri. Ez…® bizir kam bagha k…® bar akonge. Egh bar akuegh mamagh…®ra ikiam.
\s1 Pol ghaze, an angam…®ra ik…®va Filipain gumazamizibar akurvagham
\p 
\v 19 \x - \xo 1:19 \xt 2 Korin 1:11\x*K…® bar fo, ia zurara nan akurvaghasa God ko m…®gei, ez…® Krais Iesus…®n Duam gavgavim na gan…®di. Ez…® tuavir kam…®n God nan akurvaght…®, k…® kalabus ategh azenan izam. K…® bizir kam g…®fo, egh bar akuegh…®va mamagh…®ra ikiam.
\v 20 \x - \xo 1:20 \xt Rom 5:5; 8:19; Efesus 6:19-20; 1 Pita 4:16\x*Egha nan n…®ghn…®zir bar ekiam kamak…®n, k…® arazir derazir puvat…®zitam damuva an aghums…®zim inian kogham. Puvat…®. Nan n…®ghn…®zim kamak…®n, dat…®r…®gh…®n ko g…®n, k…® zuraram ami mogh…®n, atiatingan kogh…®va tugh gavgavigh arazir aghuibara damuam. Ez…® k…® angam…®ra ikiam o k…® aremegham, bizir k…® amiba bar, ziar ekiam Krais dan…®ngam.
\v 21 \x - \xo 1:21 \xt Galesia 2:20\x*Nan n…®ghn…®zim kamak…®n, k…® nguazir kam…®n itir ik…®r…®m…®rim…®n ik…®, Krais baghv…®ra ikiam. O k…® aremegh…®va, nan ovevem nan ik…®r…®m…®rir kam gafiragham.
\v 22 \x - \xo 1:22 \xt Rom 1:13\x*Egh k…® angam…®ra nguazir kam…®n ik…®v…®ra ik…®, kamagh…®n k…® gumazamizir av…®ribar akurvagham. Egh k…® tuavir manam…®n mangam? K…® fozir puvat…®.
\v 23 \x - \xo 1:23 \xt 2 Korin 5:8; 2 Timoti 4:6\x*N…®ghn…®zir pumuning na getui. K…® bar ifonge, k…® aremegh Krais ko ikiam. N…®ghn…®zir kam a bar dera.
\v 24 K…® ia bagha n…®ghn…®gha, ian akurvaghasa, kamagh…®n k…® angam…®ra ikiam.
\v 25-26 K…® kamagh…®n ifonge, k…® ua mang…® ia batogh…®va ia ko ik…®t…®, ia Krais Iesus…®n porogh…®v ik…®va k…® ia ko ikiamin bizim bagh ia na bagh bar akuegham. Kamagh…®n k…® bar fo, k…® ian akurvaghamin ingangarim ikiav…®ra iti. Eght…® k…® ik…® ia ko ingar…®va, ian akurvaght…® ia n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim ik…® egh bar akuegham.
\s1 Filipain gumazamiziba, God derav…®ra me gamima me uaghan m…®zaziba isi
\p 
\v 27 \x - \xo 1:27 \xt 1 Korin 1:10; Efesus 4:1; Filipai 4:3; Kolosi 1:10; 1 Tesalonika 2:12\x*Ez…® bar bizir ekiam kara, ian daroriba Krais…®n Akar Aghuim m…®kemez…® mogh…®n an g…®n mang…®va bar deragh ik…®. K…® kamagh…®n ifonge, k…® iz…® ian ganam, o k…® saghon ik…®va ia baragham, egh k…® fogh suam, ia tuivigha gavgavigha egha navir vam…®ra iti. Egha ia uari inigha n…®ghn…®zir vam…®ran ingarava, gumazamizibar n…®ghn…®ziba fema me n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim…®n Akar Aghuim…®n iti. Kamaghsua, k…® ghaze, ia derav…®ra daru ik…®.
\v 28 Kamagh…®n, ian apaniba ia damut…® ia atiatingan mark…®. Ia zurara uan n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim men akakaghs…® gavgafigh. Kamagh…®n me fogham, me ovengam, eght…® Godra, a uab…® ian akurvagham.
\v 29 \x - \xo 1:29 \xt Aposel 5:41; Rom 5:3; Efesus 2:8\x*Ia fogh, God derav…®ra ia gamuava ingangarim ia gan…®ngiz…®ma, ia Krais…®n ingangarim gami. Ingangarir kam, a n…®ghn…®zir gavgavimra Krais…®n itir pu. Puvat…®. Ia uaghan ingangarir kam damuva Krais…®n ziam bang…®n m…®zaziba iniam.
\v 30 \x - \xo 1:30 \xt Aposel 16:19-40; Filipai 1:13; Kolosi 2:1; 1 Tesalonika 2:2\x*Fom…®ra ia nan garima k…® m…®dorozir kam…®n aven iti. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ia nan akam barasi, k…® m…®soghav…®ra iti. Ez…® ia na ko e m…®dorozir kam…®n aven ikia, kamagh…®n, ia m…®zaziba isi.
\c 2
\s1 E bar navir vam…®ra ik…®va igharaz darazi derav…®ra me damuam
\p 
\v 1-2 Krais ti ian naviba gavgavim dagh an…®di? A ti bar ia gifuegha ia gamima ia navir am…®rizim…®n iti? Ia ti God…®n Duam ko poroghav iti? Egha ia ti igharazi darazir apangkuvigha derav…®ra me gami? Egh kamagh…®n, ia arazir aghuibar amut…®, nan agorogem bar iz…®vagham. Ia bar n…®ghn…®zir vam…®ra ik…®, egh igharaz darazigh ifongezir arazir vam…®ran g…®n mang…®. Ia bar navir vam…®ra ik…®va bizir vam…®ra bagh n…®ghn…®gh.
\v 3 \x - \xo 2:3 \xt Rom 12:10; Galesia 5:26; Efesus 5:21; Filipai 1:15-16; Jems 3:14\x*Ia uarira uarigh n…®ghn…®ghan kogham, egh uaghan ziar ekiaba inis…® ingaran mark…®. Puvat…®. Ia bar uari d…®kab…®ragh, kamagh…®n m…®k…®m suam, igharaz darazi ian p…®n iti.
\v 4 \x - \xo 2:4 \xt 1 Korin 10:24; 10:33; 13:5\x*Ia uarira uan bizibara ganan mark…®. Puvat…®. Ia uaghan vaghvagh gumazamizir igharazibar bizibar gan…®va men akurvagh.
\s1 Krais bar uab…® d…®kab…®raz…®ma, God a fe
\p 
\v 5 \x - \xo 2:5 \xt Matyu 11:29; Jon 13:15; 1 Pita 2:21; 1 Jon 2:6\x*Ia, n…®ghn…®zir Krais Iesus suirazir kamra, ia uaghan n…®ghn…®zir kamra suiraght…®ma a ian ik…®.
\v 6 \x - \xo 2:6 \xt Jon 1:1-2; 5:18; 10:33; 17:5; 2 Korin 4:4; Kolosi 1:15; Hibru 1:3\x*A guizbang…®ra God, egha an arazir God…®n m…®n itim…®n suighasa n…®ghn…®zir pu. Bar puvat…®.
\v 7 \x - \xo 2:7 \xt Jon 1:14; 2 Korin 8:9; Galesia 4:4; Hibru 2:14; 2:17\x*A uab…® arazir kam bar anetegha, pura ingangarir gumazir k…®nim…®n m…®n oto. A nguazir kam…®n gumazim…®n otoz…® gumazamiziba an garima, a guiz…®n gumazim…®n iti.
\v 8 \x - \xo 2:8 \xt Matyu 26:39; 26:42; Jon 10:17-18; Rom 8:3; Hibru 5:8; 12:2\x*Egha a uab…® d…®kab…®ragha God…®n akam baragha bar an g…®n ghua egha areme. Guizbang…®ra a gumazir bar kuram…®n m…®rara, ter ighuvim…®n areme.
\v 9 \x - \xo 2:9 \xt Jon 17:1-5; Aposel 2:33; Efesus 1:20-21; Hibru 1:3-4\x*Ez…® bizir kam bagha God Iesus fegha a isa bar p…®n anet…®. Egha God ziar bar aghuir mam a gan…®ngiz…®, ziar kam bar ziabagh afira.
\v 10 \x - \xo 2:10 \xt Matyu 28:18; Rom 14:11; Akar Mogomem 5:13\x*\x - \xo 2:10-11 \xt Aisaia 45:23\x*God kamagh…®n ifonge, God…®n Nguibam…®n itiba ko, nguazir kam…®n itiba ko, nguazim…®n apengan itiba, me bar mogh…®ra Iesus…®n damazim…®n uan tevibar ap…®righ an apengan ik…®va an ziam fam.
\v 11 \x - \xo 2:11 \xt Jon 13:13; Aposel 2:36; Rom 10:9; 1 Korin 8:6\x*Egh me bar azenan an gun kamagh…®n m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄúKrais Iesus, an Ekiam!‚Äù Egh tuavir kamra, me ziar ekiam God en Afeziam dan…®ngam. God kamaghsua, ziar bar aghuir kam Iesus gan…®ngi.
\s1 E angazangarim…®n m…®n gumazamizibar tong…®n ikiam
\p 
\v 12-13 \x - \xo 2:12-13 \xt Onger Akaba 2:11; Jon 15:5; 1 Korin 12:6; 15:10; 2 Korin 3:5; Efesus 6:5; Filipai 1:5; 2 Pita 1:5-8; 1 Tesalonika 2:13; Hibru 13:21\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…®, nan namakar aghuiba, ia zurara nan akaba barasi, ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ia uaghan kamagh…®n damu. K…® ia ko itir dughiam…®n orazi ia dera. K…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ian saghon ti, kamagh…®n ia derav…®ra nan akabar g…®n mang…®. E fo, God ian akura, egha a ian navir averiabar ingarav…®ra iti. Egha a uab…® ian n…®ghn…®ziba fema ia a ifongezir arazibagh ami, ez…® an arazir kabar amuasa gavgavim ia gan…®gav…®ra iti. Kamagh…®n, ia dat…®r…®gh…®n God…®n atiating…®va akong…®va puv…®ra ingar…®va, egh akurvazir aghuir God ia bagha at…®zir kam, a iniam.
\p 
\v 14-16 \x - \xo 2:14-16 \xt God…®n Araziba 32:5; Aisaia 49:4; Daniel 12:3; Matyu 5:14-16; 5:45; 10:16; Rom 14:1; 1 Korin 10:10; Galesia 2:2; Efesus 5:1; 5:8; Filipai 1:10; 1 Tesalonika 2:19; 3:5; 1 Pita 2:12; 4:9\x*God kamagh…®n ifonge, ia an borir bar aghuibara ikiam, egh arazir kuratam ian puvat…®ght…®, ia navir averiabar aven bar zuegham. Egh ia akar angam…®ra itim…®n suiragh, egh mati overiam…®n itir m…®koveziba isia taghtazi mogh…®n nguazir kam…®n gumazamizibar tong…®n ikiam. Kar gumazamizir arazir aghuiba ategha arazir kurabagh amiba. Bizir kam bang…®n, bizir ia bar amiba, ia n…®m…®ra ik…® dar amu. Ia akar av…®ribav k…®m, egh akabar uariv soghan mark…®. Ia kamagh…®n damut…®, Krais Ua Izamin Dughiam…®n, k…® ian araziba bagh bar akuegham. Egh k…® kamagh…®n fogham, ingangarir dafar k…® ian tong…®n amizir kaba, k…® pura dagh amizir puvat…®.
\p 
\v 17 \x - \xo 2:17 \xt Rom 15:16; 2 Timoti 4:6\x*Ian n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim, a mati ofan mam ia a isa God gan…®di. K…® foghan kogham, me ti na m…®sueght…® k…® aremeght…® me nan ghuzim ingegh…®va wain…®n ofan m…®n a inigh ian ofan kam sarama a ingegham. Bizir kam otoght…®, k…® bar akuegham. K…® guizbang…®ra ia ko, e bar mogh…®ra bar akuegham.
\v 18 \x - \xo 2:18 \xt Filipai 3:1; 4:4\x*Ez…® kamagh…®ra ia uaghan bar akongegh. Ia guizbang…®ra na ko, e bar akuegham.
\s1 Pol Filipain nguibar ekiam…®n Timoti amangasa m…®gei
\p 
\v 19 Ekiam Iesus a ifueght…®ma, k…® zuam…®ra Timoti amadaght…® a ia bagh izam. K…® ghaze, a ua iz…® ian gun na m…®k…®mam, eght…® nan navim bar deragham. Kamagh…®n, k…® anemangasa.
\v 20 Gumazir igharazitam Timotin m…®n amua na ko itir puvat…®. A na ko navir vam…®ra ikia egha zurara ian akurvaghamin tuavibagh n…®ghn…®si.
\v 21 \x - \xo 2:21 \xt 1 Korin 10:24; 10:33; 13:5; 2 Timoti 4:10; 4:16\x*Ez…® gumazir maba bar uan bizibara n…®ghn…®si, me Krais Iesus…®n ingangarim g…®n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®.
\v 22 \x - \xo 2:22 \xt 1 Korin 4:17; 1 Timoti 1:2; 2 Timoti 1:2\x*Ez…® Timoti uan ingangarir aghuim ian akaz…®, ia a g…®fogha g…®fa. Ia kamagh…®n fo, an Akar Aghuim…®n ingangarim…®n nan akurvasi, mati borim uan afeziam…®n akurvasi.
\v 23 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® tong m…®zuam egh ganigham, bizir tizimra na batogham. K…® fogh…®va egh zuam…®ra anemadaght…®ma a ia bagh mang…®gham.
\v 24 Ez…® nan n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim kamak…®n, Ekiam tuavim at…®gham, eght…® dughiar ovezim…®n k…® uaghan mang…® ian ganam.
\s1 Pol Filipain nguibar ekiam…®n Epafroditus amangasa m…®gei
\p 
\v 25 \x - \xo 2:25 \xt Filipai 4:18\x*K…® kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®gha ghaze, k…® ti en aveghbuam Epafroditus amadaght…®ma a ia bagh izam. A na ko ingarava, uaghan nan akurvagha m…®sosi. Ia faragha, a nan akurvaghasa, ia anemadaz…® a ize.
\v 26 A bar ian apangkuvigha ian ganasa bar ifonge. A fo, ia an ar…®mariar akam baraki, ez…® bizir kam a gamima a bar oseme.
\v 27 Guizbang…®ra, a faragha ar…®a, egha atam aremeghai. Ez…® God an apangkufi. Ez…® k…® fo, os…®mt…®zir bar ekiam na avaraghan God aghua. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, God anar…®ram apangkuvir puvat…®, a uaghan nan apangkufi. Kamagh…®n an a gamiz…®ma a ua dera.
\v 28 Ez…® bizir kam bagha k…® Epafroditus amangasa bar ifonge, eght…® ia an ganigh ua bar akuegham. Eght…® k…® uaghan osemeghan kogham.
\v 29-30 \x - \xo 2:29-30 \xt 1 Korin 16:16-18; Filipai 4:10; 1 Timoti 5:17\x*Kamagh…®n, ia Ekiam…®n ziam…®n Epafroditus inis…® bar akongegh. A, ingangarir ia na bagh damuan koghamim, an a gami. Kamagh…®n, a Krais…®n ingangarim gamuava atam areme. A derav…®ra ikiasa uab…® g…®n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®. Egha uan ar…®mariam adogha ingangarim gamuav…®ra iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia ziar ekiam a dan…®ng uaghan an m…®raram amir gumazamiziba sara ziar ekiam me dan…®ng.
\c 3
\s1 Gumazir n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Krais…®n itim, a God…®n damazim…®n dera
