\v 1 \x - \xo 3:1 \xt 2 Korin 13:11; Filipai 2:18; 4:4\x*Nan adarasi, k…® uan m…®g…®r…®g…®am ag…®vasa kamagh…®n ia m…®gei, ia Ekiam ko poroghav ik…®, egh ia bar akongegh. K…® fo, k…® faragh osirizir akaba, da ian akurvasi. Kamagh…®n, k…® ua ia bagha akar kabara osiran am…®razir puvat…®.
