\v 2 \x - \xo 3:2 \xt Onger Akaba 22:16; 22:20; Rom 2:28; 2 Korin 11:13; Galesia 5:2; 5:15; Akar Mogomem 22:15\x*Ia arazir kurabagh amir gumaziba bagh gan, me afiar atiabar m…®n arazir m…®z…®r…®zibagh ami. Gumazir kaba ghaze, e bar Israel…®n arazim…®n g…®n mang…® uan m…®karziba aghor…®va dagh as…®ghas…®gham.\f + \fr 3:2 \ft Gumazir maba ti gumazamizibav g…®a ghaze, dughiar me Krais…®n anav…®n otozim, me Israel…®n Arazibar g…®n mang…®va, gumaziba uan m…®karzir mogomebar iniba aghoram. Pol bar gumazir kabar m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam…®n aghua, egha kamagh…®n Filipaiba derav…®ra me bagh ganasa m…®g…®r…®g…®ar gavgavim me gan…®ngi.\f*
\v 3 \x - \xo 3:3 \xt Rom 2:29\x*Erara guizbang…®n m…®karzir mogomebar iniba aghorir arazim…®n g…®n zuir darasi. Ez…® me puvat…®. Erara God…®n Duam…®n akurvazim…®n uari isa God ganigha Krais Iesus ko poroghav ikia bar akonge. E fo, arazir gumaziba uan m…®karzibar amiba, da tong men akuraghan kogham, ez…® e n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim dar itir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, e fo, erara guizbang…®n m…®karzir mogomebar iniba aghorir arazim…®n g…®n zuir darasi.\f + \fr 3:3 \ft Fom…®ra Israelia m…®karzir mogomebar inibar ghori, ez…® arazir kam men akagha ghaze, me God…®n adarazir otifi. Dat…®r…®gh…®n e m…®karzir mogomebar inibar ghorir puvat…®. Akar kam, ‚Äúm…®karzir mogomebar iniba aghorir arazim…®n g…®n zuir darasi,‚Äù an akar is…®n zuim ghaze, ‚Äúme God…®n adarasi.‚Äù Egha dat…®r…®gh…®n, guizbang…®n God…®n adarasi, me Krais…®n adarasi. Ez…® akar kam, ‚Äúguizbang…®n m…®karzir mogomebar iniba aghorir arazim…®n g…®n zuir darasi,‚Äù kar e Krais…®n adarasi.\f*
\v 4 \x - \xo 3:4 \xt 2 Korin 11:18; 11:21-29\x*Ia oragh. Arazir gumaziba uan m…®karzibar amiba, da en akurvaght…®, kamagh…®n k…® uab…® k…® derav…®ra ikiam. Gumazitam uan m…®karzim…®n otivir biziba bagh n…®ghn…®gh n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim dar ik…®t…®, k…® kamagh…®n ia m…®k…®mam, nan otivizir biziba, an otivizir biziba bar dagh afira.
\v 5 \x - \xo 3:5 \xt Luk 1:59; Aposel 23:6; 26:5; Rom 11:1; 2 Korin 11:22\x*Nan amebam na batez…®, 7plan dughiaba g…®vaz…®, me namba 8…®n dughiam…®n nan m…®karzir mogomem…®n inim atu. Nan afeziam ko amebam, aning Israel…®n gumazim ko amizim, ez…® k…® Israel…®n gumazir mam. K…® Benjamin…®n adarazir gumazir mam. K…® Hibrun akam m…®gei, ez…® nan inazafeziaba uakan. K…® Farisin gumazimra, egha Moses Osirizir Araziba bar derav…®ra dar g…®n zui.
\v 6 \x - \xo 3:6 \xt Aposel 8:3; 22:4; 26:9-11\x*K…® fom…®ra bar gavgavigha God…®n ingangarim damuasa bar ifonge, kamagh…®n k…® Krais…®n adarazigh as…®ghas…®gha m…®zazim me gan…®di. Ez…® gumaziba Moses Osirizir Arazibagh n…®ghn…®gha, nan araziba tuis…®gha, me fo, os…®mt…®zitam nan itir puvat…®.
