\v 8 \x - \xo 3:8 \xt Jeremaia 9:23-24; 1 Korin 2:2; Kolosi 2:2\x*K…® Judan bizibara m…®geir pu. Puvat…®. K…® Krais Iesus g…®fo a nan Ekiam, ez…® k…® fofozir kam g…®n…®ghn…®gha ghaze, a guizbang…®n bizim, ez…® nguazir kam…®n biziba bar pura m…®neghm…®nezir k…®niba. K…® Kraisra g…®n mangasa ifonge. Egha bizir igharaziba bar da ategh, k…® Krais…®n suiragh,
\v 9 \x - \xo 3:9 \xt Rom 3:21-22; 9:30; 10:3-6; Galesia 2:16\x*egh a ko bar porogh ikiam. K…® Moses Osirizir Arazibar g…®n ghua, gumazir aghuim…®n otivasa n…®ghn…®zir pu. Puvat…®. K…® tuavir igharazim…®n ghua God…®n damazim…®n derazir gumazim…®n oto, kar n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Krais…®n itir tuavim. E n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Krais…®n itima, God uab…® ghaze, e an damazim…®n dera.
