\v 12 \x - \xo 3:12 \xt Aposel 9:5-6; 1 Timoti 6:12; 6:19; Hibru 12:23\x*K…® kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®, k…® Krais Iesus…®n arazim inigha g…®vagha, gumazir aghuim…®n otogha g…®fa. Puvat…®. K…® zurara ingangarir gavgavim gamua arazir kam…®n suizi mogh…®n, Krais nan suira.
