\v 15 \x - \xo 3:15 \xt 1 Korin 2:6; 14:20; Galesia 5:10\x*Eght…® e gumazir Krais…®n arazibar g…®n ghua gumazir aruabar n…®ghn…®ziba itiba, e bar n…®ghn…®zir k…® gun m…®kemezir kam…®n g…®n mangam. Egh ia n…®ghn…®zir igharazim ik…®t…®, God ian n…®ghn…®zir derazir puvat…®zir kam, ian akagham.
\v 16 \x - \xo 3:16 \xt Rom 12:16; 15:5; Galesia 6:16\x*Ez…® n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba e da inigha g…®fa, e pamtem…®n dar suiragham. Bizir kam a bizir ekiam.
