\v 1 \x - \xo 4:1 \xt 1 Tesalonika 2:19-20\x*Kamagh…®n, nan adarasi, ia Ekiam ko porogh…®v ik…® tuivigh gavgafigh. K…® uan navim isa ia gan…®ngi! K…® ian saghon ikia, ia bagha puv…®ra n…®ghn…®si! K…® ian arazir aghuibar gun igharaz daraziv gei! Egha k…® ia bagha bar akonge, nan namakar aghuiba!
