\v 7 \x - \xo 4:7 \xt Aisaia 26:3; Jon 14:27; Rom 5:1; Kolosi 3:15\x*Eght…® kamagh…®n God ia damut…® ia navir am…®rizim…®n ikiam. Egh ia Krais Iesus ko porogh deragh ikiam, eght…® tuavir kam…®n God…®n navir am…®rizim derav…®ra ian naviba ko n…®ghn…®zibagh eghuvt…® da bar derav…®ra ikiam. God navir am…®rizir e gan…®ngizir kam, a bar bizir aghuim, ez…® navir am…®rizir kam gumazibar fofozim bar a gafira.
